714627f-a.title: Manhattan: 82nd Street - Central Park West
714627f-a.text:
82nd Street, at adjoining and west of the N.W. corner of Central Park West. This view also shows Central Park West, West Side,
north from and including 82nd Street.
October 20, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
